      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant delivers 414 hp with a staggering 8,400 RPM redline, utilizing eight individual throttle bodies for exceptional transient response. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the M-Variable Differential Lock, providing precise torque vectoring and lateral stability. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the critical rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system and valvetrain operate smoothly. The 6-speed manual transmission retains its tactile, short-throw engagement. A mechanically robust example with a clean subframe, ready for spirited canyon runs or track day duty.",
